{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Build a full “Ambassador Program” landing page for a lash supply brand (Studio Lume Supplies). The brand aesthetic is luxury-minimal, beige + white, clean spacing, soft shadows, refined typography. Tone is approachable premium (polished but not corporate).

    PAGE GOAL:
    Make it instantly clear there are 2 tiers:
    1) LUME Collective = entry level
    2) LUME Elite = most exclusive
    Elite includes everything in Collective + extra benefits and exclusivity.
    Keep hierarchy obvious and skimmable.

    LAYOUT / SECTIONS (in this order):

    1) HERO (top)
    - Left aligned on desktop, centered on mobile
    - Heading: “LUME Ambassador Program”
    - Subheading: “Choose your tier, enjoy perks, earn rewards, and get featured by Studio Lume Supplies.”
    - Small trust line under subheading (small caps): “For certified lash artists & beauty professionals”
    - Primary button: “Apply Now” (scrolls to application section)
    - Secondary text link: “Compare tiers” (scrolls to tier comparison)

    2) QUICK SUMMARY STRIP (thin, elegant)
    - 3 short icon items (simple line icons):
      - “Perks & Discounts”
      - “Referral Rewards”
      - “Featured Content”
    Keep it subtle, not loud.

    3) TIER COMPARISON (main focus)
    - Two cards side-by-side (stack on mobile)
    - Make Elite visually higher: slightly lifted card, “Most Exclusive” badge in top-right.
    - Card style: white background, soft shadow, thin border, rounded corners.
    - Each card includes:
      A) Tier name
      B) One-line description (not long)
      C) “Best for…” micro-line (small text)
      D) Benefits list (check icons)
      E) Commitment list (small dot icons or subtle icons)
      F) Tier button

    TIER 1: LUME Collective (Entry level)
    - Description: “Entry level perks + community.”
    - Best for: “Artists who want to trial + post casually.”
    Benefits (checks):
    - “15% off storewide (personal use)”
    - “Early access to sales”
    - “Surprise order extras”
    - “Ambassador-only promos”
    - “Birthday reward”
    - “Eligible to upgrade to Elite”
    Commitment (subtle bullets):
    - “Add @studiolumesupplies to your Instagram bio”
    - “Tag us when using our products”
    - “No exclusivity required”
    Button: “Apply for Collective”

    TIER 2: LUME Elite (Most Exclusive)
    - Badge: “Most Exclusive”
    - Description: “Priority perks + brand representation.”
    - Best for: “Consistent creators who want more.”
    Benefits (checks) – FIRST LINE MUST BE:
    - “Everything in LUME Collective”
    Then:
    - “20% off storewide (personal use)”
    - “Referral code to share (followers/clients)”
    - “Reward: every 10 referrals = 30% off code”
    - “Early access to launches + sales”
    - “Priority reposting”
    - “Birthday reward”
    Commitment (subtle bullets):
    - “Add @studiolumesupplies to your Instagram bio”
    - “Tag us in all professional content using our products”
    - “Exclusive representation: you may buy other brands, but don’t promote them”
    Button: “Apply for Elite”

    Add a small helper note under the tier cards:
    “Not sure where you fit? Start in Collective — upgrade opportunities available.”

    4) HOW IT WORKS (simple 3 steps)
    - Three clean steps with numbers:
      1. “Apply”
      2. “Get approved + receive your perks”
      3. “Post, share, and earn rewards”
    Keep copy short.

    5) FAQ (accordion style, minimal)
    Include 6 FAQs:
    - “How do I apply?”
    - “How long does approval take?”
    - “Can I upgrade from Collective to Elite?”
    - “Do I need to post a minimum amount?”
    - “Can I be an ambassador if I use other brands?”
    - “How do referral rewards work?”

    6) FINAL CTA (application)
    - Heading: “Ready to join?”
    - Short line: “Apply below — we review applications regularly.”
    - Two buttons side-by-side:
      - “Apply for Collective”
      - “Apply for Elite”
    Buttons link to separate application forms or the same form with a dropdown.

    DESIGN RULES:
    - Use plenty of whitespace.
    - Use beige accents, black/charcoal text, and soft grey dividers.
    - No loud gradients, no neon, no clutter.
    - Typography: elegant sans-serif, clear hierarchy (H1 big, H2 medium, body readable).
    - Mobile first: cards stack, buttons full width, clean spacing.
    - Use subtle icons only (thin line style).
    - Keep the page feeling “beauty clinic / luxury minimal”.

    OUTPUT:
    Generate the blocks/sections for this page with appropriate headings, text, and buttons, matching the structure above.

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-ambassador-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: {{ block.settings.desktop_width_percent }}%;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px {{ block.settings.horizontal_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    display: block;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size }}px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: {{ block.settings.text_color }};
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_text }};
    border: 1px solid {{ block.settings.button_bg }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.button_radius }}px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_text }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_hover_bg }};
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__btn--secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_text }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_border }};
  }

  .ai-ambassador-cta__btn--secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_hover_bg }};
    color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_hover_text }};
    border-color: {{ block.settings.button_secondary_hover_bg }};
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-ambassador-cta__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.heading_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-ambassador-cta__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .ai-ambassador-cta__btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-ambassador-cta-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-ambassador-cta__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    {% if block.settings.heading != blank %}
      <h2 class="ai-ambassador-cta__heading-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
    {% endif %}

    {% if block.settings.subtext != blank %}
      <p class="ai-ambassador-cta__subtext-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ block.settings.subtext }}</p>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="ai-ambassador-cta__buttons-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% if block.settings.button_1_text != blank %}
        <a href="{{ block.settings.button_1_link }}" class="ai-ambassador-cta__btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.button_1_text }}
        </a>
      {% endif %}

      {% if block.settings.button_2_text != blank %}
        <a href="{{ block.settings.button_2_link }}" class="ai-ambassador-cta__btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-ambassador-cta__btn--secondary-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          {{ block.settings.button_2_text }}
        </a>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

